channel.title: Trouble downloading swf file
channel.description: Well I have trouble downloading the swf file from the link below: http://novelconcepts.co.uk/FlashElementTD/ The problem is that I used a video downloader to download the swf file. The program gave me the link: http://novelconcepts.co.uk/FlashElementTDv2007-01-15.swf?embed=3 This of course is not the right link as there should not be the embed=3 following it. When I tried the same thing again without the embed thing the page does not load. If anyone knows how to resolve this problem and would kindly upload the file, that would be much appreciated. Thanks.
